{"tid":534470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【戰鬥民族】零下6度浸湖水 普京面不改容","createTime":"2018-01-19T21:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T11:06:05.000Z","uid":37666,"like":251,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"5d85aaaa1bc497a3648a5fda5169a4441aa0953c","tid":534470,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T21:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/origin/595c0006191ce470a400\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp1.pstatp.com%2Forigin%2F595c0006191ce470a400&h=a9adf717&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">65歲</span>的俄羅斯總統普京1​​8日在零下溫度的嚴寒中進入冰水中洗浴，慶祝主顯節。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯衛星網報導，普京當天完成於聖彼得堡和列寧格勒州的工作安排後前往特維爾州，在那裡參觀了尼爾&mdash;斯托洛佈內男修道院，並參加了主顯節洗浴，浸入謝利格爾湖的冰窟窿裡。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯總統新聞秘書佩斯科夫說：&ldquo;正值主顯節，普京來到禮拜儀式部分，並參加了在謝利格爾湖的主顯節洗浴。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n據佩斯科夫稱，今年俄中部未出現傳統上的主顯節嚴寒，因此&ldquo;湖區的溫度約為零下6至7度&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n他還說，這不是普京第一次參加洗禮節了，&ldquo;總統都下湖好幾年了&rdquo;。但報導稱，這是克里姆林宮首次對外公佈普京在冰窟中洗浴的照片。"},{"pid":"e733a55c08978e978a9dee50f1d1c0ab1669aca9","tid":534470,"uid":123711,"like":6,"dislike":63,"score":-57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T21:33:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d1b4a335c532b2d0f31e54e2f8339528fe932de","tid":534470,"uid":146707,"like":79,"dislike":0,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T21:35:56.000Z","msg":"最近天氣開始轉涼了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89942f2d2fc4e33a5c378da1b098fbab6519c825","tid":534470,"uid":37666,"like":141,"dislike":4,"score":137,"quote":{"pid":"e733a55c08978e978a9dee50f1d1c0ab1669aca9","tid":534470,"uid":123711,"like":6,"dislike":63,"score":-57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T21:33:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T21:54:43.000Z","msg":"65歲算咁上下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i1.wp.com/inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/1932969711/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.co