4470,"uid":129054,"like":58,"dislike":3,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T08:55:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc8a4fe561f9f2ed333698d3f11dc369d54638b3","tid":534470,"uid":105034,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T08:58:29.000Z","msg":"肯定係同一個普京？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7241e75dbb4f4f9c20ab24cb845d37476cb5869f","tid":534470,"uid":52595,"like":43,"dislike":5,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T09:03:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82bae72dba44fe46da9315b2b17e8bc218cdf8b2","tid":534470,"uid":26038,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T09:23:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十五度，西班牙人穿大衣、戴手套；<span style=\"color: red;\">普京</span>作日光浴。<br />\n<br />\n十度，法國人開暖氣；<span style=\"color: red;\">普京</span>在花園裡種花。<br />\n<br />\n五度，義大利人發不動車子，<span style=\"color: red;\">普京</span>開敞篷車遊街。<br />\n<br />\n零下五度，加州人凍斃了；<span style=\"color: red;\">普京</span>在戶外烤肉。<br />\n<br />\n零下十度，英國人開暖氣；<span style=\"color: red;\">普京</span>開始穿長袖。<br />\n<br />\n零下五十度，北極熊撤離北極；西伯利亞軍隊延後冬季野外求生訓練，等待真正的冬天到來。<br />\n<br />\n零下一百八十三度，食物中的微生物死亡；西伯利亞牛隻抱怨酪農的手太冰。<br />\n<br />\n零下兩百七十三度，原子停止活動；<span style=\"color: red;\">普京</span>終於說：『老天，外面好冷！』<br />\n<br />\n連登仔：『網絡世界幸好沒有溫度！』</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4460c27b447fb8512cfeba2a472b9cde0f685681","tid":534470,"uid":92178,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T09:27:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98fff82a7f5286f4a1a769c74c6a80317b5d07f9","tid":534470,"uid":11097,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T09:49:06.000Z","msg":"香港D廢老呢"},{"pid":"c1f2f4a0c968bd522d357d423055b7d8e173fbe1","tid":534470,"uid":114275,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T09:51:53.000Z","msg":"d 肌肉 .... 唉叫連登仔情可以堪"},{"pid":"42cc3ef7396847e97e6e474a8e501167e3a9bf06","tid":534470,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T09:54:14.000Z","msg":"<blockq